 Job Registration Form Validation

 Description
This project is a Job Registration Form that validates the name, email, and contact number using regular expressions. If all inputs are valid, the message **"Registered Successfully"** is displayed; otherwise, appropriate error messages are shown.

 Technologies Used
* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript

How to Run
Open `index.html` in any web browser, fill in the form, and submit to check the validation.
